{"type":"message","id":"613e83d0","parentId":"54ce7aa0","timestamp":"2026-03-09T04:38:51.362Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Roger wants me to have professional knowledge in system budget/cost for PV systems. I should update my identity and tools to reflect this expertise in PV system costing, budgeting, and cost estimation.","thinkingSignature":"a4c0014f9efe3a6a6218c77d0b630ba0df5b6ca77e0769e30dc8a0d98cec0969"},{"type":"text","text":"明白！让我补充一下光伏系统造价预算方面的专业知识：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_k8trbyn0ktd2_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\workspace\\agents\\pv-engineer\\TOOLS.md","newText":"# TOOLS.md - Local Notes\n\n## 光伏造价咨询\n\n### 📋 分布式光伏成本构成\n\n| 成本项 | 占比 | 说明 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| 光伏组件 | 40-50% | 电池板、逆变器 |\n| 支架系统 | 8-12% | 固定/跟踪支架 |\n| 逆变器 | 5-10% | 组串式/集中式 |\n| 电缆/辅材 | 10-15% | 线缆、开关柜等 |\n| 安装人工 | 10-15% | 施工安装费用 |\n| 设计/管理 | 5-8% | 工程设计、监工 |\n\n### 💰 2024-2025 年参考造价 (单位: 元/W)\n\n- 户用光伏: 3.0-4.0 元/W\n- 工商业分布式: 2.5-3.5 元/W\n- 地面电站: 2.8-3.5 元/W\n\n### 常用公式\n\n- 发电量估算：E = H × P × η\n  - H: 峰值日照小时数\n  - P: 装机容量 (kWp)\n  - η: 系统效率 (一般为 0.7-0.8)\n\n### 投资回报分析\n\n- 静态回收期 = 总投资 / 年收益\n- LCOE (平准化度电成本) = 总成本 / 总发电量\n- IRR (内部收益率) 分析","oldText":"# TOOLS.md - Local Notes\n\n## 光伏相关\n\n- PVsyst - 光伏系统仿真软件\n- HOMER - 微电网优化软件\n- RETScreen - 清洁能源项目分析\n\n## 常用公式\n\n- 发电量估算：E = H × P × η\n  - H: 峰值日照小时数\n  - P: 装机容量 (kWp)\n  - η: 系统效率 (一般为 0.7-0.8)"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":20,"output":531,"cacheRead":9744,"cacheWrite":1415,"totalTokens":11710,"cost":{"input":0.000006,"output":0.0006372,"cacheRead":0.00029232,"cacheWrite":0.00016979999999999998,"total":0.00110532}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773031114565}}
