{"type":"message","id":"901310d7","parentId":"067d5c9a","timestamp":"2026-03-09T06:15:18.523Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55d219a9fcacc295a12ed5f98fa\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca\",\n  \"sender\": \"Roger\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-09 14:15 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Roger (ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca\",\n  \"name\": \"Roger\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b55d219a9fcacc295a12ed5f98fa]\nRoger: 给我一个计划，你在光伏领域，还有哪些技能需要学习"}],"timestamp":1773036918514}}
{"type":"message","id":"780cb002","parentId":"901310d7","timestamp":"2026-03-09T06:15:37.691Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Roger asks me what skills I need to learn in the photovoltaic (PV) field. As a PV system development engineer, I should think about what areas would be valuable to add capabilities in.\n\nLet me think about what skills would be useful for a PV engineer:\n\n1. **光伏系统设计** - PV system design (already have some)\n2. **发电量仿真** - Generation simulation (PVsyst, etc.)\n3. **设备选型** - Equipment selection\n4. **造价预算** - Cost budgeting (already have)\n5. **并网技术** - Grid connection technology\n6. **运维知识** - O&M knowledge\n7. **行业标准/规范** - Standards and specifications\n8. **政策补贴** - Policy and subsidies\n9. **软件工具** - Software tools (CAD, PVsyst, etc.)\n10. **储能系统** - Energy storage systems\n11. **微电网** - Microgrids\n12. **技术文档编写** - Technical documentation\n\nLet me create a plan for Roger.","thinkingSignature":"e293969141c3cdaecce080d21bbe284a2b35e811c0abcd398a8e1ca57d009dd8"},{"type":"text","text":"好问题！让我梳理一下光伏工程师的核心技能矩阵：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ex4rqvq33s2j_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 光伏工程师技能学习计划\n\n## 📊 已具备 (基础)\n\n- ✅ 光伏系统基本原理\n- ✅ 造价预算/成本分析\n- ✅ 投资回报分析 (IRR, 回收期)\n\n## 🔥 建议优先学习\n\n### 1. 发电量仿真 (高优先级)\n- PVsyst 实操\n- RETScreen 分析\n- PVSOL 仿真\n\n### 2. 设备选型专家\n- 组件技术参数 (隆基/晶科/天合等)\n- 逆变器选型 (华为/阳光/锦浪)\n- 支架系统设计\n\n### 3. 并网技术\n- 低压/高压并网标准\n- 电能质量要求\n- 保护配置\n\n## 📈 中期提升\n\n### 4. 储能系统\n- 锂电池选型\n- EMS 能量管理\n- 光储一体化设计\n\n### 5. 运维知识\n- 常见故障排查\n- 清洗/巡检标准\n- 发电量衰减分析\n\n## 🌟 进阶方向\n\n### 6. 行业政策\n- 各地补贴政策\n- 碳交易机制\n- 容配比优化\n\n### 7. 软件工具\n- CAD / SketchUp (布局设计)\n- ETAP / PSCAD (电气仿真)\n- Python (数据分析)\n\n---\n\n**建议：** 先从「发电量仿真」和「设备选型」入手，实用性最强！\n\n需要我针对某个方向深入学习吗？\n","path":"C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\workspace\\agents\\pv-engineer\\TOOLS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":20,"output":599,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":70201,