{"type":"message","id":"d468d11a","parentId":"50eda069","timestamp":"2026-03-09T14:57:59.857Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Roger 问的是如何在飞书群里加入多个机器人。这是一个关于飞书使用的问题。\n\n让我用飞书相关的技能来回答这个问题。我记得有 feishu-doc, feishu-drive, feishu-perm, feishu-wiki 这些技能，但可能没有关于群组管理的。\n\n不过这算是通用知识问题，我可以基于了解来回答：\n\n1. 飞书群最多可以添加多少个机器人？\n2. 如何添加多个机器人到群？\n\n让我先搜索一下记忆里有没有相关信息。","thinkingSignature":"d5593fd2a6e15b4c17871912118201b256c2b0347151c744d6cb88fb0fc9c24e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_onuepko47kdo_1","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"飞书群 机器人 添加 多个"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":20,"output":138,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":71369,"totalTokens":71527,"cost":{"input":0.000006,"output":0.0001656,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.008564279999999999,"total":0.008735879999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773068270270}}
{"type":"message","id":"a76e8553","parentId":"d468d11a","timestamp":"2026-03-09T14:58:00.098Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_onuepko47kdo_1","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [],\n  \"provider\": \"none\",\n  \"citations\": \"auto\",\n  \"mode\": \"fts-only\"\n}"}],"details":{"results":[],"provider":"none","citations":"auto","mode":"fts-only"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773068279987}}
{"type":"message","id":"64d3abae","parentId":"a76e8553","timestamp":"2026-03-09T14:58:26.369Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"没有相关内容，直接回答Roger的问题吧。","thinkingSignature":"f793a509d0d70429bbc1366c7185ebdc883141e86925e7458d2ec1c5655a08bc"},{"type":"text","text":"根据飞书的限制：\n\n## 飞书群添加机器人\n\n### 📌 数量限制\n- **单个群最多 50 个机器人**\n\n### 🛠️ 添加方法\n\n**方法1：群设置添加**\n1. 打开飞书群 → 点击右上角「...」\n2. 设置 → 群机器人 → 添加机器人\n3. 选择需要的机器人（自定义机器人或官方应用）\n\n**方法2：通过应用中心**\n1. 群设置 → 群机器人 → 添加\n2. 搜索「自定义机器人」\n3. 复制 Webhook 地址自行开发\n\n**方法3：管理员后台**\n- 企业管理员在「工作台 → 审批」中添加应用到群\n\n### ⚠️ 注意事项\n\n- 每个机器人需要单独获取 Webhook 或授权\n- 机器人发消息有频率限制（一般 20条/分钟）\n- 群主可踢出/禁言机器人\n\n---\n\n你是想往群里加什么功能的机器人？我可以帮你配置～ 🤖"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":62749,"output":216,"cacheRead":8821,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71786,"cost":{"input":0.0188247,"output":0.0002592,"cacheRead":0.00026462999999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01934853}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773068280099}}
